'''弗氏盐'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式 (K<sub>4</sub>[ON(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>]<sub>2</sub>)，有时写作 (K<sub>2</sub>[NO(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>])。它是一种亮黄棕色固体，但水溶液是亮紫色的。<ref>{{Greenwood&Earnshaw2nd}}</ref><ref name="chemistris.tripod.com"/> 相关的钠盐'''亚硝基二磺酸钠'''（简称NDS，化学式 Na<sub>2</sub>ON(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，[[CAS号|CAS号]] 29554-37-8）也被称为弗氏盐。<ref name=OS/>

== 应用==
弗氏盐作为一种长寿命的自由基，是[[电子自旋共振|电子自旋共振]] (EPR) 的标准。其强烈的EPR谱线由三条等强度的线主导，间距约为 13 [[高斯_(单位)|G]]（1.3 [[特斯拉|mT]]）。<ref>{{cite book | vauthors = Wertz JE, Bolton JR | title = Electron Spin Resonance: Elementary Theory and Practical Applications | year = 1972 | publisher = McGraw-Hill | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-07-069454-5 }} See page 463 for information on intensity measurements and page 86 for an EPR spectrum of Frémy's salt.</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite journal | vauthors = Colacicchi S, Carnicelli V, Gualtieri G, Di Giulio A | title =  EPR study of Frémy's salt nitroxide reduction by ascorbic acid; influence of bulk pH values | journal =  Res. Chem. Intermed. | volume =  26 | issue =  9 | pages =  885–896 | year =  2000 | doi = 10.1163/156856700X00372| s2cid = 98775951 }}</ref><ref name="Zielonka, Jacek 2005 853–863">{{cite journal | vauthors = Zielonka J, Zhao H, Xu Y, Kalyanaraman B | title = Mechanistic similarities between oxidation of hydroethidine by Frémy's salt and superoxide: stopped-flow optical and EPR studies | journal = Free Radical Biology & Medicine | volume = 39 | issue = 7 | pages = 853–863 | date = October 2005 | doi = 10.1016/j.freeradbiomed.2005.05.001 | pmid = 16140206 }}</ref>

弗氏盐可用于某些氧化反应，例如某些苯胺或苯酚的氧化。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Zimmer H, Lankin DC, Horgan SW | title = Oxidations with potassium nitrosodisulfonate (Frémy's radical). Teuber reaction. | journal = Chemical Reviews | year = 1971 | volume = 71 | issue = 2 | pages = 229–246 | doi = 10.1021/cr60270a005 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Islam I, Skibo EB, Dorr RT, Alberts DS | title = Structure-activity studies of antitumor agents based on pyrrolo[1,2-''a'']benzimidazoles: new reductive alkylating DNA cleaving agents | journal = Journal of Medicinal Chemistry | volume = 34 | issue = 10 | pages = 2954–2961 | date = October 1991 | pmid = 1920349 | doi = 10.1021/jm00114a003 }}</ref><ref name=Teuber1>{{cite journal | vauthors = Teuber HJ, Benz S | journal = [[Chemische_Berichte|Chem. Ber.]] | url = http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/fulltext/112293483/PDFSTART | volume = 100 | pages = 2918–2929 | title = Reaktionen mit Nitrosodisulfonat, XXXVI. Chinolin-chinone-(5.6) aus 5-Hydroxy-chinolinen | issue = 9 | year = 1967 | doi = 10.1002/cber.19671000916 | language = de }}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref name=Teuber2>{{cite journal| vauthors = Teuber HJ | title = Use of dipotassium nitrosodisulfonate (Frémy's salt): 4,5-dimethyl-''o''-benzoquinone | doi= 10.15227/orgsyn.052.0088| volume= 52 | page= 88 | year = 1972|journal=Org. Synth.}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Xue W, Warshawsky D, Rance M, Jayasimhulu K | title =  A metabolic activation mechanism of 7''H''-dibenzo[''c'',''g'']carbozole via ''o''-quinone. Part 1: synthesis of 7''H''-dibenzo[''c'',''g'']carbozole-3,4-dione and reactions with nucleophiles | journal =  Polycyclic Aromatic Compounds | volume =  22 | issue = 3–4 | pages =  295–300 | year =  2002| doi = 10.1080/10406630290026957 | s2cid = 95507636 }}</ref>它也允许肽和基于肽的{{le|水凝胶|Hydrogel}}的聚合和交联。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Wilchek M, Miron T | title = Mussel-inspired new approach for polymerization and cross-linking of peptides and proteins containing tyrosines by Frémy's salt oxidation | journal = Bioconjugate Chemistry | volume = 26 | issue = 3 | pages = 502–510 | date = March 2015 | pmid = 25692389 | doi = 10.1021/bc5006152 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Fichman G, Schneider JP | title = Utilizing Frémy's Salt to Increase the Mechanical Rigidity of Supramolecular Peptide-Based Gel Networks | language = en | journal = Frontiers in Bioengineering and Biotechnology | volume = 8 | pages = 594258 | date = 2021 | pmid = 33469530 | pmc = 7813677 | doi = 10.3389/fbioe.2020.594258 | doi-access = free }}</ref>

它还可以用作研究中过氧自由基的模型，以研究各种天然产品中抗氧化作用的机制。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Liu ZL, Han ZX, Chen P, Liu YC | title = Stopped-flow ESR study on the reactivity of vitamin E, vitamin C and its lipophilic derivatives towards Frémy's salt in micellar systems | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_chemistry-and-physics-of-lipids_1990-11_56_1/page/73 | journal = Chemistry and Physics of Lipids | volume = 56 | issue = 1 | pages = 73–80 | date = November 1990 | pmid = 1965427 | doi = 10.1016/0009-3084(90)90090-E }}</ref>

== 制备==
弗氏盐可以由[[羟胺二磺酸|羟胺二磺酸]]开始制备而成。[[氧化|氧化]]它的[[共轭碱|共轭碱]]可以得到紫色的[[双阴离子|双阴离子]]：

:HON(SO<sub>3</sub>H)<sub>2</sub>  →   [HON(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>2−</sup>  +  2 H<sup>+</sup>
:2 [HON(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>2−</sup>  +  PbO<sub>2</sub>   →     2 [ON(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>2−</sup>  +  PbO  +  H<sub>2</sub>O

[[羟胺二磺酸盐|羟胺二磺酸盐]]则是由[[亚硝酸盐|亚硝酸盐]]和[[亚硫酸氢盐|亚硫酸氢盐]]反应而成的。氧化反应通常是在低温下进行的，可以通过化学方法或[[电解|电解]]达成。<ref name=OS>{{cite journal | vauthors = Wehrli PA, Pigott F | title = Oxidation with the nitrosodisulfonate radical. I. Preparation and use of sodium nitrosodisulfonate: trimethyl-''p''-benzoquinone | journal = Organic Syntheses | doi = 10.15227/orgsyn.052.0083 | page = 83 | volume = 52 | year = 1972 }}</ref><ref name="chemistris.tripod.com">{{cite web | title = Synthesis and Characterization of Potassium Nitrosodisulfonate, Frémy's Salt | url = http://chemistris.tripod.com/science/synthesis_of_fremys_salt.pdf | work = tripod.com | access-date = 2021-12-03 | archive-date = 2010-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100923031529/http://chemistris.tripod.com/science/synthesis_of_fremys_salt.pdf }}</ref>

其它制备方法：

: HNO<sub>2</sub> + 2 {{chem|HSO|3|-}} → {{chem|HON(SO|3|)|2|2-}} + H<sub>2</sub>O
: 3 {{chem|HON(SO|3|)|2|2-}} + {{chem|MnO|4|-}} + H<sup>+</sup>  →  3 {{chem|ON(SO|3|)|2|2-}} + MnO<sub>2</sub> + 2 H<sub>2</sub>O
: 2 {{chem|ON(SO|3|)|2|2-}} + 4 K<sup>+</sup> → K<sub>4</sub>[ON(SO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>]<sub>2</sub>

==历史==
弗氏盐是在1845年由[[埃德蒙·弗雷米|埃德蒙·弗雷米]] (1814–1894)发现的。<ref>参见：
*  Frémy, E. (1845) [http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uva.x002489033;view=1up;seq=412 "Sur un nouvelle série d'acides formés d'oxygène, de soufre, d'hydrogène et de d'azote"] {{Wayback|url=http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uva.x002489033;view=1up;seq=412 |date=20211203081329 }} (On a new series of acids formed from oxygen, sulfur, hydrogen, and nitrogen), ''Annales de Chimie et de Physique'', 3rd series, '''15''' : 408-488.  Frémy's salt appears on [http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uva.x002489033;view=1up;seq=451 p. 447] {{Wayback|url=http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uva.x002489033;view=1up;seq=451 |date=20211203081421 }}, where it's called ''"sulfazidate de potasse"''.
* Frémy, E. (1845) [https://books.google.com/books?id=k3RPAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA218#v=onepage&q&f=false "Sur un nouvelle série d'acides formés d'oxygène, de soufre, d'hydrogène et de d'azote"] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=k3RPAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA218#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20220417152959 }} (On a new series of acids formed from oxygen, sulfur, hydrogen, and nitrogen), ''Comptes rendus'', '''21''' : 218–226.  This is a condensed version of the article that appeared in ''Annales de Chimie et de Physique''.
* "Séances académiques," ''L'Institut'', no. 604, 23 July 1845, [https://books.google.com/books?id=wY88AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA265#v=onepage&q&f=false pp. 265–266.] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wY88AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA265#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20220425090812 }} 
* "Séances académiques," ''L'Institut'', no. 619, 12 November 1845, [https://books.google.com/books?id=wY88AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA393#v=onepage&q&f=false pp. 393.] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wY88AAAAcAAJ&pg=PA393#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20220425090818 }}  Here a committee of the French Academy of Sciences reviewed Frémy's findings.
*  Edward Divers and Tamemasa Haga (1900) [http://www.mocavo.co.uk/Journal-of-the-Chemical-Society-Great-Britain-1900-Volume-74/362288/463#458 "Identification and constitution of Frémy's sulphazotised salts of potassium,"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mocavo.co.uk/Journal-of-the-Chemical-Society-Great-Britain-1900-Volume-74/362288/463#458 |date=20160206085724 }} ''Journal of the Chemical Society, Transactions'', '''77''' :  440-446. [https://dx.doi.org/10.1039/CT9007700440 doi:10.1039/CT9007700440] Here, correct formulae for Frémy's salts are presented.  On [http://www.mocavo.co.uk/Journal-of-the-Chemical-Society-Great-Britain-1900-Volume-74/362288/463#463 p. 445] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mocavo.co.uk/Journal-of-the-Chemical-Society-Great-Britain-1900-Volume-74/362288/463#463 |date=20160206085724 }}, the salt that Frémy called ''sulfazidate'' is identified as ON(SO<sub>3</sub>K)<sub>2</sub>.</ref>

